   *(The sweet spot between bare and full-art. Daisy tips along the smile line, sage green or pastel yellow tips with white daisies, blooming gel accents on French nails — the most wearable format for florals that works on short and medium lengths. Skill level: beginner-intermediate. The 2026 shift: the classic white tip is being replaced by floral tip variations. Occasions: work, garden parties, everyday. Can DIY or salon.)*

